{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sc-callout",
      "x": -560, "y": -560, "width": 900, "height": 80,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "> [!note] 🎬\n> Screenplay HQ — pitch it in one line, break the story into acts and beats, storyboard the key scene panel by panel, and track every scene to a locked draft.",
      "color": "#8B5CF6",
      "ib": { "kind": "callout", "id": "sc-callout", "text": "Screenplay HQ — pitch it in one line, break the story into acts and beats, storyboard the key scene panel by panel, and track every scene to a locked draft.", "icon": "🎬", "color": "#8B5CF6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-grp-core",
      "x": -560, "y": -440, "width": 400, "height": 300,
      "type": "group",
      "label": "Story Core",
      "color": "#14B8A6",
      "ib": { "kind": "group", "id": "sc-grp-core", "label": "Story Core", "color": "#14B8A6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-logline",
      "x": -530, "y": -385, "width": 340, "height": 110,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "🎯 LOGLINE\nWhen [inciting incident], a [flawed protagonist] must [objective] before [stakes/deadline].",
      "color": "#FEF3C7",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-logline", "text": "🎯 LOGLINE\nWhen [inciting incident], a [flawed protagonist] must [objective] before [stakes/deadline].", "color": "#FEF3C7" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-theme",
      "x": -530, "y": -260, "width": 340, "height": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "💭 THEME\nWhat is this story really about? State it as an argument, not a topic.",
      "color": "#DBEAFE",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-theme", "text": "💭 THEME\nWhat is this story really about? State it as an argument, not a topic.", "color": "#DBEAFE" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-characters",
      "x": -120, "y": -440, "width": 460, "height": 300,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### Characters\n\n| Name | Role | Want | Need |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Rae Chen | Protagonist | Win the case | Forgive herself |\n| Marcus Hale | Antagonist | Bury the truth | Be seen |\n|  | Supporting |  |  |",
      "color": "#FFFFFF",
      "ib": {
        "kind": "table",
        "id": "sc-characters",
        "title": "Characters",
        "color": "#FFFFFF",
        "columns": [
          { "id": "ch-name", "label": "Name", "type": "text" },
          { "id": "ch-role", "label": "Role", "type": "select", "options": [
            { "label": "Protagonist", "color": "#3B82F6" },
            { "label": "Antagonist", "color": "#DC2626" },
            { "label": "Supporting", "color": "#6B7280" }
          ] },
          { "id": "ch-want", "label": "Want", "type": "text" },
          { "id": "ch-need", "label": "Need", "type": "text" }
        ],
        "rows": [
          { "id": "chr-1", "cells": { "ch-name": "Rae Chen", "ch-role": "Protagonist", "ch-want": "Win the case", "ch-need": "Forgive herself" } },
          { "id": "chr-2", "cells": { "ch-name": "Marcus Hale", "ch-role": "Antagonist", "ch-want": "Bury the truth", "ch-need": "Be seen" } },
          { "id": "chr-3", "cells": { "ch-name": "", "ch-role": "Supporting", "ch-want": "", "ch-need": "" } }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-video",
      "x": 380, "y": -440, "width": 420, "height": 240,
      "type": "link",
      "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KxDwieKpawg",
      "ib": { "kind": "bookmark", "id": "sc-video", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KxDwieKpawg" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-act1",
      "x": -560, "y": -80, "width": 340, "height": 280,
      "type": "group",
      "label": "Act I — Setup",
      "color": "#3B82F6",
      "ib": { "kind": "group", "id": "sc-act1", "label": "Act I — Setup", "color": "#3B82F6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-a1-beat1",
      "x": -535, "y": -15, "width": 290, "height": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Opening image — the world before. Mirror it in the final image.",
      "color": "#DBEAFE",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-a1-beat1", "text": "Opening image — the world before. Mirror it in the final image.", "color": "#DBEAFE" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-a1-beat2",
      "x": -535, "y": 95, "width": 290, "height": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Catalyst (~p.12) — the event that breaks the routine. No going back.",
      "color": "#DBEAFE",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-a1-beat2", "text": "Catalyst (~p.12) — the event that breaks the routine. No going back.", "color": "#DBEAFE" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-act2",
      "x": -180, "y": -80, "width": 340, "height": 280,
      "type": "group",
      "label": "Act II — Confrontation",
      "color": "#F59E0B",
      "ib": { "kind": "group", "id": "sc-act2", "label": "Act II — Confrontation", "color": "#F59E0B" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-a2-beat1",
      "x": -155, "y": -15, "width": 290, "height": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Midpoint (~p.55) — false victory or false defeat. Stakes double.",
      "color": "#FEF3C7",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-a2-beat1", "text": "Midpoint (~p.55) — false victory or false defeat. Stakes double.", "color": "#FEF3C7" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-a2-beat2",
      "x": -155, "y": 95, "width": 290, "height": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "All is lost (~p.75) — the worst moment. Whiff of death.",
      "color": "#FEF3C7",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-a2-beat2", "text": "All is lost (~p.75) — the worst moment. Whiff of death.", "color": "#FEF3C7" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-act3",
      "x": 200, "y": -80, "width": 340, "height": 280,
      "type": "group",
      "label": "Act III — Resolution",
      "color": "#DC2626",
      "ib": { "kind": "group", "id": "sc-act3", "label": "Act III — Resolution", "color": "#DC2626" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-a3-beat1",
      "x": 225, "y": -15, "width": 290, "height": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Climax — the protagonist proves they've changed by choosing the need over the want.",
      "color": "#FEE2E2",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-a3-beat1", "text": "Climax — the protagonist proves they've changed by choosing the need over the want.", "color": "#FEE2E2" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-a3-beat2",
      "x": 225, "y": 95, "width": 290, "height": 90,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Final image — the world after. The opening image, transformed.",
      "color": "#FEE2E2",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-a3-beat2", "text": "Final image — the world after. The opening image, transformed.", "color": "#FEE2E2" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-grp-storyboard",
      "x": -560, "y": 260, "width": 1100, "height": 340,
      "type": "group",
      "label": "Storyboard — Key Scene",
      "color": "#8B5CF6",
      "ib": { "kind": "group", "id": "sc-grp-storyboard", "label": "Storyboard — Key Scene", "color": "#8B5CF6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-panel-1",
      "x": -530, "y": 320, "width": 240, "height": 220,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "PANEL 1 — WIDE\n\nEstablish the space. One image, one idea.\n\n🖼️ Paste a frame sketch or reference still here.",
      "color": "#F3F4F6",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-panel-1", "text": "PANEL 1 — WIDE\n\nEstablish the space. One image, one idea.\n\n🖼️ Paste a frame sketch or reference still here.", "color": "#F3F4F6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-panel-2",
      "x": -270, "y": 320, "width": 240, "height": 220,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "PANEL 2 — MEDIUM\n\nCharacter enters in motion — what are they doing, not saying?",
      "color": "#F3F4F6",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-panel-2", "text": "PANEL 2 — MEDIUM\n\nCharacter enters in motion — what are they doing, not saying?", "color": "#F3F4F6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-panel-3",
      "x": -10, "y": 320, "width": 240, "height": 220,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "PANEL 3 — CLOSE-UP\n\nThe detail that matters: hands, eyes, the object everything turns on.",
      "color": "#F3F4F6",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-panel-3", "text": "PANEL 3 — CLOSE-UP\n\nThe detail that matters: hands, eyes, the object everything turns on.", "color": "#F3F4F6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-panel-4",
      "x": 250, "y": 320, "width": 240, "height": 220,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "PANEL 4 — OVER-THE-SHOULDER\n\nThe confrontation. What do they see — and what do we see that they don't?",
      "color": "#F3F4F6",
      "ib": { "kind": "sticky", "id": "sc-panel-4", "text": "PANEL 4 — OVER-THE-SHOULDER\n\nThe confrontation. What do they see — and what do we see that they don't?", "color": "#F3F4F6" }
    },
    {
      "id": "sc-beats",
      "x": -560, "y": 660, "width": 560, "height": 400,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "### Beat Sheet\n\n| Beat | Act | Page | Status |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Opening image | I | 1 | To write |\n| Catalyst | I | 12 | To write |\n| Break into two | I | 25 | To write |\n| Midpoint | II | 55 | To write |\n| All is lost | II | 75 | To write |\n| Break into three | III | 85 | To write |\n| Finale | III | 110 | To write |",
      "color": "#FFFFFF",
      "ib": {
        "kind": "table",
        "id": "sc-beats",
        "title": "Beat Sheet",
        "color": "#FFFFFF",
        "columns": [
          { "id": "bt-beat", "label": "Beat", "type": "text" },
          { "id": "bt-act", "label": "Act", "type": "select", "align": "center", "options": [
